      svā̱doḥ phala̍sya ja̱gdhvāya̍ yathā̱kāma̱ṁ ni pa̍dyate || 10.146.05

      āñja̍nagandhiṁ sura̱bhiṁ ba̍hva̱nnāmakṛ̍ṣīvalām |

      prāhaṁ mṛ̱gāṇā̍ṁ mā̱tara̍maraṇyā̱nima̍śaṁsiṣam || 10.146.06


      śratte̍ dadhāmi pratha̱māya̍ ma̱nyave'ha̱nyadvṛ̱traṁ narya̍ṁ vi̱vera̱paḥ |

      u̱bhe yattvā̱ bhava̍to̱ roda̍sī̱ anu̱ reja̍te̱ śuṣmā̍tpṛthi̱vī ci̍dadrivaḥ || 10.147.01

      tvaṁ mā̱yābhi̍ranavadya mā̱yina̍ṁ śravasya̱tā mana̍sā vṛ̱trama̍rdayaḥ |

      tvāminnaro̍ vṛṇate̱ gavi̍ṣṭiṣu̱ tvāṁ viśvā̍su̱ havyā̱sviṣṭi̍ṣu || 10.147.02

      aiṣu̍ cākandhi puruhūta sū̱riṣu̍ vṛ̱dhāso̱ ye ma̍ghavannāna̱śurma̱gham |

      arca̍nti to̱ke tana̍ye̱ pari̍ṣṭiṣu me̱dhasā̍tā vā̱jina̱mahra̍ye̱ dhane̍ || 10.147.03

      sa innu rā̱yaḥ subhṛ̍tasya cākana̱nmada̱ṁ yo a̍sya̱ raṁhya̱ṁ cike̍tati |

      tvāvṛ̍dho maghavandā̱śva̍dhvaro ma̱kṣū sa vāja̍ṁ bharate̱ dhanā̱ nṛbhi̍ḥ || 10.147.04

      tvaṁ śardhā̍ya mahi̱nā gṛ̍ṇā̱na u̱ru kṛ̍dhi maghavañcha̱gdhi rā̱yaḥ |

      tvaṁ no̍ mi̱tro varu̍ṇo̱ na mā̱yī pi̱tvo na da̍sma dayase vibha̱ktā || 10.147.05


      su̱ṣvā̱ṇāsa̍ indra stu̱masi̍ tvā sasa̱vāṁsa̍śca tuvinṛmṇa̱ vāja̍m |

      ā no̍ bhara suvi̱taṁ yasya̍ cā̱kantmanā̱ tanā̍ sanuyāma̱ tvotā̍ḥ || 10.148.01

      ṛ̱ṣvastvami̍ndra śūra jā̱to dāsī̱rviśa̱ḥ sūrye̍ṇa sahyāḥ |

      guhā̍ hi̱taṁ guhya̍ṁ gū̱ḻhama̱psu bi̍bhṛ̱masi̍ pra̱srava̍ṇe̱ na soma̍m || 10.148.02

      a̱ryo vā̱ giro̍ a̱bhya̍rca vi̱dvānṛṣī̍ṇā̱ṁ vipra̍ḥ suma̱tiṁ ca̍kā̱naḥ |

      te syā̍ma̱ ye ra̱ṇaya̍nta̱ somai̍re̱nota tubhya̍ṁ rathoḻha bha̱kṣaiḥ || 10.148.03

      i̱mā brahme̍ndra̱ tubhya̍ṁ śaṁsi̱ dā nṛbhyo̍ nṛ̱ṇāṁ śū̍ra̱ śava̍ḥ |

      tebhi̍rbhava̱ sakra̍tu̱ryeṣu̍ cā̱kannu̱ta trā̍yasva gṛṇa̱ta u̱ta stīn || 10.148.04

      śru̱dhī hava̍mindra śūra̱ pṛthyā̍ u̱ta sta̍vase ve̱nyasyā̱rkaiḥ |

      ā yaste̱ yoni̍ṁ ghṛ̱tava̍nta̱masvā̍rū̱rmirna nimnairdra̍vayanta̱ vakvā̍ḥ || 10.148.05


      sa̱vi̱tā ya̱ntraiḥ pṛ̍thi̱vīma̍ramṇādaskambha̱ne sa̍vi̱tā dyāma̍dṛṁhat |

      aśva̍mivādhukṣa̱ddhuni̍ma̱ntari̍kṣama̱tūrte̍ ba̱ddhaṁ sa̍vi̱tā sa̍mu̱dram || 10.149.01

      yatrā̍ samu̱draḥ ska̍bhi̱to vyauna̱dapā̍ṁ napātsavi̱tā tasya̍ veda |

      ato̱ bhūrata̍ ā̱ utthi̍ta̱ṁ rajo'to̱ dyāvā̍pṛthi̱vī a̍prathetām || 10.149.02

      pa̱ścedama̱nyada̍bhava̱dyaja̍tra̱mama̍rtyasya̱ bhuva̍nasya bhū̱nā |

      su̱pa̱rṇo a̱ṅga sa̍vi̱turga̱rutmā̱npūrvo̍ jā̱taḥ sa u̍ a̱syānu̱ dharma̍ || 10.149.03

      gāva̍ iva̱ grāma̱ṁ yūyu̍dhiri̱vāśvā̍nvā̱śreva̍ va̱tsaṁ su̱manā̱ duhā̍nā |

      pati̍riva jā̱yāma̱bhi no̱ nye̍tu dha̱rtā di̱vaḥ sa̍vi̱tā vi̱śvavā̍raḥ || 10.149.04

      hira̍ṇyastūpaḥ savita̱ryathā̍ tvāṅgira̱so ju̱hve vāje̍ a̱smin |

      e̱vā tvārca̱nnava̍se̱ vanda̍māna̱ḥ soma̍syevā̱ṁśuṁ prati̍ jāgarā̱ham || 10.149.05


      sami̍ddhaści̱tsami̍dhyase de̱vebhyo̍ havyavāhana |

      ā̱di̱tyai ru̱drairvasu̍bhirna̱ ā ga̍hi mṛḻī̱kāya̍ na̱ ā ga̍hi || 10.150.01

      i̱maṁ ya̱jñami̱daṁ vaco̍ jujuṣā̱ṇa u̱pāga̍hi |

      martā̍sastvā samidhāna havāmahe mṛḻī̱kāya̍ havāmahe || 10.150.02

      tvāmu̍ jā̱tave̍dasaṁ vi̱śvavā̍raṁ gṛṇe dhi̱yā |

      agne̍ de̱vā ā va̍ha naḥ pri̱yavra̍tānmṛḻī̱kāya̍ pri̱yavra̍tān || 10.150.03

      a̱gnirde̱vo de̱vānā̍mabhavatpu̱rohi̍to̱'gniṁ ma̍nu̱ṣyā̱3̱̍ ṛṣa̍ya̱ḥ samī̍dhire |

      a̱gniṁ ma̱ho dhana̍sātāva̱haṁ hu̍ve mṛḻī̱kaṁ dhana̍sātaye || 10.150.04

      a̱gniratri̍ṁ bha̱radvā̍ja̱ṁ gavi̍ṣṭhira̱ṁ prāva̍nna̱ḥ kaṇva̍ṁ tra̱sada̍syumāha̱ve |

      a̱gniṁ vasi̍ṣṭho havate pu̱rohi̍to mṛḻī̱kāya̍ pu̱rohi̍taḥ || 10.150.05


      śra̱ddhayā̱gniḥ sami̍dhyate śra̱ddhayā̍ hūyate ha̱viḥ |

      śra̱ddhāṁ bhaga̍sya mū̱rdhani̱ vaca̱sā ve̍dayāmasi || 10.151.01

      pri̱yaṁ śra̍ddhe̱ dada̍taḥ pri̱yaṁ śra̍ddhe̱ didā̍sataḥ |

      pri̱yaṁ bho̱jeṣu̱ yajva̍svi̱daṁ ma̍ udi̱taṁ kṛ̍dhi || 10.151.02

      yathā̍ de̱vā asu̍reṣu śra̱ddhāmu̱greṣu̍ cakri̱re |

      e̱vaṁ bho̱jeṣu̱ yajva̍sva̱smāka̍mudi̱taṁ kṛ̍dhi || 10.151.03

      śra̱ddhāṁ de̱vā yaja̍mānā vā̱yugo̍pā̱ upā̍sate |

      śra̱ddhāṁ hṛ̍da̱yya1̱̍yākū̍tyā śra̱ddhayā̍ vindate̱ vasu̍ || 10.151.04

      śra̱ddhāṁ prā̱tarha̍vāmahe śra̱ddhāṁ ma̱dhyaṁdi̍na̱ṁ pari̍ |

      śra̱ddhāṁ sūrya̍sya ni̱mruci̱ śraddhe̱ śraddhā̍paye̱ha na̍ḥ || 10.151.05


      śā̱sa i̱tthā ma̱hā a̍syamitrakhā̱do adbhu̍taḥ |

      na yasya̍ ha̱nyate̱ sakhā̱ na jīya̍te̱ kadā̍ ca̱na || 10.152.01

      sva̱sti̱dā vi̱śaspati̍rvṛtra̱hā vi̍mṛ̱dho va̱śī |

      vṛṣendra̍ḥ pu̱ra e̍tu naḥ soma̱pā a̍bhayaṁka̱raḥ || 10.152.02

      vi rakṣo̱ vi mṛdho̍ jahi̱ vi vṛ̱trasya̱ hanū̍ ruja |

      vi ma̱nyumi̍ndra vṛtrahanna̱mitra̍syābhi̱dāsa̍taḥ || 10.152.03

      vi na̍ indra̱ mṛdho̍ jahi nī̱cā ya̍ccha pṛtanya̱taḥ |

      yo a̱smā a̍bhi̱dāsa̱tyadha̍raṁ gamayā̱ tama̍ḥ || 10.152.04

      ape̍ndra dviṣa̱to mano'pa̱ jijyā̍sato va̱dham |

      vi ma̱nyoḥ śarma̍ yaccha̱ varī̍yo yavayā va̱dham || 10.152.05


      ī̱ṅkhaya̍ntīrapa̱syuva̱ indra̍ṁ jā̱tamupā̍sate |

      bhe̱jā̱nāsa̍ḥ su̱vīrya̍m || 10.153.01

      tvami̍ndra̱ balā̱dadhi̱ saha̍so jā̱ta oja̍saḥ |

      tvaṁ vṛ̍ṣa̱nvṛṣeda̍si || 10.153.02

      tvami̍ndrāsi vṛtra̱hā vya1̱̍ntari̍kṣamatiraḥ |

      uddyāma̍stabhnā̱ oja̍sā || 10.153.03

      tvami̍ndra sa̱joṣa̍sama̱rkaṁ bi̍bharṣi bā̱hvoḥ |

      vajra̱ṁ śiśā̍na̱ oja̍sā || 10.153.04

      tvami̍ndrābhi̱bhūra̍si̱ viśvā̍ jā̱tānyoja̍sā |

      sa viśvā̱ bhuva̱ ābha̍vaḥ || 10.153.05


      soma̱ eke̍bhyaḥ pavate ghṛ̱tameka̱ upā̍sate |

      yebhyo̱ madhu̍ pra̱dhāva̍ti̱ tāści̍de̱vāpi̍ gacchatāt || 10.154.01

      tapa̍sā̱ ye a̍nādhṛ̱ṣyāstapa̍sā̱ ye sva̍rya̱yuḥ |

      tapo̱ ye ca̍kri̱re maha̱stāści̍de̱vāpi̍ gacchatāt || 10.154.02

      ye yudhya̍nte pra̱dhane̍ṣu̱ śūrā̍so̱ ye ta̍nū̱tyaja̍ḥ |

      ye vā̍ sa̱hasra̍dakṣiṇā̱stāści̍de̱vāpi̍ gacchatāt || 10.154.03

      ye ci̱tpūrva̍ ṛta̱sāpa̍ ṛ̱tāvā̍na ṛtā̱vṛdha̍ḥ |

      pi̱tṝntapa̍svato yama̱ tāści̍de̱vāpi̍ gacchatāt || 10.154.04

      sa̱hasra̍ṇīthāḥ ka̱vayo̱ ye go̍pā̱yanti̱ sūrya̍m |

      ṛṣī̱ntapa̍svato yama tapo̱jā api̍ gacchatāt || 10.154.05


      arā̍yi̱ kāṇe̱ vika̍ṭe gi̱riṁ ga̍ccha sadānve |

      śi̱rimbi̍ṭhasya̱ satva̍bhi̱stebhi̍ṣṭvā cātayāmasi || 10.155.01

      ca̱tto i̱taśca̱ttāmuta̱ḥ sarvā̍ bhrū̱ṇānyā̱ruṣī̍ |

      a̱rā̱yya̍ṁ brahmaṇaspate̱ tīkṣṇa̍śṛṇgodṛ̱ṣanni̍hi || 10.155.02

      a̱do yaddāru̱ plava̍te̱ sindho̍ḥ pā̱re a̍pūru̱ṣam |

      tadā ra̍bhasva durhaṇo̱ tena̍ gaccha parasta̱ram || 10.155.03

      yaddha̱ prācī̱raja̍ga̱ntoro̍ maṇḍūradhāṇikīḥ |

      ha̱tā indra̍sya̱ śatra̍va̱ḥ sarve̍ budbu̱dayā̍śavaḥ || 10.155.04

      parī̱me gāma̍neṣata̱ parya̱gnima̍hṛṣata |

      de̱veṣva̍krata̱ śrava̱ḥ ka i̱mā ā da̍dharṣati || 10.155.05


      a̱gniṁ hi̍nvantu no̱ dhiya̱ḥ sapti̍mā̱śumi̍vā̱jiṣu̍ |

      tena̍ jeṣma̱ dhana̍ṁdhanam || 10.156.01

      yayā̱ gā ā̱karā̍mahe̱ sena̍yāgne̱ tavo̱tyā |

      tāṁ no̍ hinva ma̱ghatta̍ye || 10.156.02

      āgne̍ sthū̱raṁ ra̱yiṁ bha̍ra pṛ̱thuṁ goma̍ntama̱śvina̍m |

      a̱ṅdhi khaṁ va̱rtayā̍ pa̱ṇim || 10.156.03

      agne̱ nakṣa̍trama̱jara̱mā sūrya̍ṁ rohayo di̱vi |

      dadha̱jjyoti̱rjane̍bhyaḥ || 10.156.04

      agne̍ ke̱turvi̱śāma̍si̱ preṣṭha̱ḥ śreṣṭha̍ upastha̱sat |

      bodhā̍ sto̱tre vayo̱ dadha̍t || 10.156.05


      i̱mā nu ka̱ṁ bhuva̍nā sīṣadhā̱mendra̍śca̱ viśve̍ ca de̱vāḥ || 10.157.01

      ya̱jñaṁ ca̍ nasta̱nva̍ṁ ca pra̱jāṁ cā̍di̱tyairindra̍ḥ sa̱ha cī̍kḷpāti || 10.157.02

      ā̱di̱tyairindra̱ḥ saga̍ṇo ma̱rudbhi̍ra̱smāka̍ṁ bhūtvavi̱tā ta̱nūnā̍m || 10.157.03

      ha̱tvāya̍ de̱vā asu̍rā̱nyadāya̍nde̱vā de̍va̱tvama̍bhi̱rakṣa̍māṇāḥ || 10.157.04

      pra̱tyañca̍ma̱rkama̍naya̱ñchacī̍bhi̱rāditsva̱dhāmi̍ṣi̱rāṁ parya̍paśyan || 10.157.05


      sūryo̍ no di̱vaspā̍tu̱ vāto̍ a̱ntari̍kṣāt |

      a̱gnirna̱ḥ pārthi̍vebhyaḥ || 10.158.01

      joṣā̍ savita̱ryasya̍ te̱ hara̍ḥ śa̱taṁ sa̱vā arha̍ti |

      pā̱hi no̍ di̱dyuta̱ḥ pata̍ntyāḥ || 10.158.02

      cakṣu̍rno de̱vaḥ sa̍vi̱tā cakṣu̍rna u̱ta parva̍taḥ |

      cakṣu̍rdhā̱tā da̍dhātu naḥ || 10.158.03

      cakṣu̍rno dhehi̱ cakṣu̍ṣe̱ cakṣu̍rvi̱khyai ta̱nūbhya̍ḥ |

      saṁ ce̱daṁ vi ca̍ paśyema || 10.158.04

      su̱sa̱ṁdṛśa̍ṁ tvā va̱yaṁ prati̍ paśyema sūrya |

      vi pa̍śyema nṛ̱cakṣa̍saḥ || 10.158.05


      uda̱sau sūryo̍ agā̱duda̱yaṁ mā̍ma̱ko bhaga̍ḥ |

      a̱haṁ tadvi̍dva̱lā pati̍ma̱bhya̍sākṣi viṣāsa̱hiḥ || 10.159.01

      a̱haṁ ke̱tura̱haṁ mū̱rdhāhamu̱grā vi̱vāca̍nī |

      mamedanu̱ kratu̱ṁ pati̍ḥ sehā̱nāyā̍ u̱pāca̍ret || 10.159.02

      mama̍ pu̱trāḥ śa̍tru̱haṇo'tho̍ me duhi̱tā vi̱rāṭ |

      u̱tāhama̍smi saṁja̱yā patyau̍ me̱ śloka̍ utta̱maḥ || 10.159.03

      yenendro̍ ha̱viṣā̍ kṛ̱tvyabha̍vaddyu̱mnyu̍tta̱maḥ |

      i̱daṁ tada̍kri devā asapa̱tnā kilā̍bhuvam || 10.159.04

      a̱sa̱pa̱tnā sa̍patna̱ghnī jaya̍ntyabhi̱bhūva̍rī |

      āvṛ̍kṣama̱nyāsā̱ṁ varco̱ rādho̱ asthe̍yasāmiva || 10.159.05

      sama̍jaiṣami̱mā a̱haṁ sa̱patnī̍rabhi̱bhūva̍rī |

      yathā̱hama̱sya vī̱rasya̍ vi̱rājā̍ni̱ jana̍sya ca || 10.159.06


      tī̱vrasyā̱bhiva̍yaso a̱sya pā̍hi sarvara̱thā vi harī̍ i̱ha mu̍ñca |

      indra̱ mā tvā̱ yaja̍mānāso a̱nye ni rī̍rama̱ntubhya̍mi̱me su̱tāsa̍ḥ || 10.160.01

      tubhya̍ṁ su̱tāstubhya̍mu̱ sotvā̍sa̱stvāṁ gira̱ḥ śvātryā̱ ā hva̍yanti |

      indre̱dama̱dya sava̍naṁ juṣā̱ṇo viśva̍sya vi̱dvā i̱ha pā̍hi̱ soma̍m || 10.160.02

      ya u̍śa̱tā mana̍sā̱ soma̍masmai sarvahṛ̱dā de̱vakā̍maḥ su̱noti̍ |

      na gā indra̱stasya̱ parā̍ dadāti praśa̱stamiccāru̍masmai kṛṇoti || 10.160.03

      anu̍spaṣṭo bhavatye̱ṣo a̍sya̱ yo a̍smai re̱vānna su̱noti̱ soma̍m |

      nira̍ra̱tnau ma̱ghavā̱ taṁ da̍dhāti brahma̱dviṣo̍ ha̱ntyanā̍nudiṣṭaḥ || 10.160.04

      a̱śvā̱yanto̍ ga̱vyanto̍ vā̱jaya̍nto̱ havā̍mahe̱ tvopa̍ganta̱vā u̍ |

      ā̱bhūṣa̍ntaste suma̱tau navā̍yāṁ va̱yami̍ndra tvā śu̱naṁ hu̍vema || 10.160.05


      mu̱ñcāmi̍ tvā ha̱viṣā̱ jīva̍nāya̱ kama̍jñātaya̱kṣmādu̱ta rā̍jaya̱kṣmāt |

      grāhi̍rja̱grāha̱ yadi̍ vai̱tade̍na̱ṁ tasyā̍ indrāgnī̱ pra mu̍muktamenam || 10.161.01

      yadi̍ kṣi̱tāyu̱ryadi̍ vā̱ pare̍to̱ yadi̍ mṛ̱tyora̍nti̱kaṁ nī̍ta e̱va |

      tamā ha̍rāmi̱ nirṛ̍teru̱pasthā̱daspā̍rṣamenaṁ śa̱taśā̍radāya || 10.161.02

      sa̱ha̱srā̱kṣeṇa̍ śa̱taśā̍radena śa̱tāyu̍ṣā ha̱viṣāhā̍rṣamenam |

      śa̱taṁ yathe̱maṁ śa̱rado̱ nayā̱tīndro̱ viśva̍sya duri̱tasya̍ pā̱ram || 10.161.03

      śa̱taṁ jī̍va śa̱rado̱ vardha̍mānaḥ śa̱taṁ he̍ma̱ntāñcha̱tamu̍ vasa̱ntān |

      śa̱tami̍ndrā̱gnī sa̍vi̱tā bṛha̱spati̍ḥ śa̱tāyu̍ṣā ha̱viṣe̱maṁ puna̍rduḥ || 10.161.04

      āhā̍rṣa̱ṁ tvāvi̍daṁ tvā̱ puna̱rāgā̍ḥ punarnava |

      sarvā̍ṅga̱ sarva̍ṁ te̱ cakṣu̱ḥ sarva̱māyu̍śca te'vidam || 10.161.05


      brahma̍ṇā̱gniḥ sa̍ṁvidā̱no ra̍kṣo̱hā bā̍dhatāmi̱taḥ |

      amī̍vā̱ yaste̱ garbha̍ṁ du̱rṇāmā̱ yoni̍mā̱śaye̍ || 10.162.01

      yaste̱ garbha̱mamī̍vā du̱rṇāmā̱ yoni̍mā̱śaye̍ |

      a̱gniṣṭaṁ brahma̍ṇā sa̱ha niṣkra̱vyāda̍manīnaśat || 10.162.02

      yaste̱ hanti̍ pa̱taya̍ntaṁ niṣa̱tsnuṁ yaḥ sa̍rīsṛ̱pam |

      jā̱taṁ yaste̱ jighā̍ṁsati̱ tami̱to nā̍śayāmasi || 10.162.03

      yasta̍ ū̱rū vi̱hara̍tyanta̱rā dampa̍tī̱ śaye̍ |

      yoni̱ṁ yo a̱ntarā̱reḻhi̱ tami̱to nā̍śayāmasi || 10.162.04

      yastvā̱ bhrātā̱ pati̍rbhū̱tvā jā̱ro bhū̱tvā ni̱padya̍te |

      pra̱jāṁ yaste̱ jighā̍ṁsati̱ tami̱to nā̍śayāmasi || 10.162.05

      yastvā̱ svapne̍na̱ tama̍sā mohayi̱tvā ni̱padya̍te |

      pra̱jāṁ yaste̱ jighā̍ṁsati̱ tami̱to nā̍śayāmasi || 10.162.06


      a̱kṣībhyā̍ṁ te̱ nāsi̍kābhyā̱ṁ karṇā̍bhyā̱ṁ chubu̍kā̱dadhi̍ |

      yakṣma̍ṁ śīrṣa̱ṇya̍ṁ ma̱stiṣkā̍jji̱hvāyā̱ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.01

      grī̱vābhya̍sta u̱ṣṇihā̍bhya̱ḥ kīka̍sābhyo anū̱kyā̍t |

      yakṣma̍ṁ doṣa̱ṇya1̱̍maṁsā̍bhyāṁ bā̱hubhyā̱ṁ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.02

      ā̱ntrebhya̍ste̱ gudā̍bhyo vani̱ṣṭhorhṛda̍yā̱dadhi̍ |

      yakṣma̱ṁ mata̍snābhyāṁ ya̱knaḥ plā̱śibhyo̱ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.03

      ū̱rubhyā̍ṁ te aṣṭhī̱vadbhyā̱ṁ pārṣṇi̍bhyā̱ṁ prapa̍dābhyām |

      yakṣma̱ṁ śroṇi̍bhyā̱ṁ bhāsa̍dā̱dbhaṁsa̍so̱ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.04

      meha̍nādvana̱ṁkara̍ṇā̱lloma̍bhyaste na̱khebhya̍ḥ |

      yakṣma̱ṁ sarva̍smādā̱tmana̱stami̱daṁ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.05

      aṅgā̍daṅgā̱llomno̍lomno jā̱taṁ parva̍ṇiparvaṇi |

      yakṣma̱ṁ sarva̍smādā̱tmana̱stami̱daṁ vi vṛ̍hāmi te || 10.163.06


      ape̍hi manasaspa̱te'pa̍ krāma pa̱raśca̍ra |

      pa̱ro nirṛ̍tyā̱ ā ca̍kṣva bahu̱dhā jīva̍to̱ mana̍ḥ || 10.164.01

      bha̱draṁ vai vara̍ṁ vṛṇate bha̱draṁ yu̍ñjanti̱ dakṣi̍ṇam |

      bha̱draṁ vai̍vasva̱te cakṣu̍rbahu̱trā jīva̍to̱ mana̍ḥ || 10.164.02

      yadā̱śasā̍ ni̱ḥśasā̍bhi̱śaso̍pāri̱ma jāgra̍to̱ yatsva̱panta̍ḥ |

      a̱gnirviśvā̱nyapa̍ duṣkṛ̱tānyaju̍ṣṭānyā̱re a̱smadda̍dhātu || 10.164.03

      yadi̍ndra brahmaṇaspate'bhidro̱haṁ carā̍masi |

      prace̍tā na āṅgira̱so dvi̍ṣa̱tāṁ pā̱tvaṁha̍saḥ || 10.164.04

      ajai̍ṣmā̱dyāsa̍nāma̱ cābhū̱mānā̍gaso va̱yam |

      jā̱gra̱tsva̱pnaḥ sa̍ṁka̱lpaḥ pā̱po yaṁ dvi̱ṣmastaṁ sa ṛ̍cchatu̱ yo no̱ dveṣṭi̱ tamṛ̍cchatu || 10.164.05


      devā̍ḥ ka̱pota̍ iṣi̱to yadi̱cchandū̱to nirṛ̍tyā i̱damā̍ja̱gāma̍ |

      tasmā̍ arcāma kṛ̱ṇavā̍ma̱ niṣkṛ̍ti̱ṁ śaṁ no̍ astu dvi̱pade̱ śaṁ catu̍ṣpade || 10.165.01

      śi̱vaḥ ka̱pota̍ iṣi̱to no̍ astvanā̱gā de̍vāḥ śaku̱no gṛ̱heṣu̍ |

      a̱gnirhi vipro̍ ju̱ṣatā̍ṁ ha̱virna̱ḥ pari̍ he̱tiḥ pa̱kṣiṇī̍ no vṛṇaktu || 10.165.02

      he̱tiḥ pa̱kṣiṇī̱ na da̍bhātya̱smānā̱ṣṭryāṁ pa̱daṁ kṛ̍ṇute agni̱dhāne̍ |

      śaṁ no̱ gobhya̍śca̱ puru̍ṣebhyaścāstu̱ mā no̍ hiṁsīdi̱ha de̍vāḥ ka̱pota̍ḥ || 10.165.03

      yadulū̍ko̱ vada̍ti mo̱ghame̱tadyatka̱pota̍ḥ pa̱dama̱gnau kṛ̱ṇoti̍ |

      yasya̍ dū̱taḥ prahi̍ta e̱ṣa e̱tattasmai̍ ya̱māya̱ namo̍ astu mṛ̱tyave̍ || 10.165.04

      ṛ̱cā ka̱pota̍ṁ nudata pra̱ṇoda̱miṣa̱ṁ mada̍nta̱ḥ pari̱ gāṁ na̍yadhvam |

      sa̱ṁyo̱paya̍nto duri̱tāni̱ viśvā̍ hi̱tvā na̱ ūrja̱ṁ pra pa̍tā̱tpati̍ṣṭhaḥ || 10.165.05


      ṛ̱ṣa̱bhaṁ mā̍ samā̱nānā̍ṁ sa̱patnā̍nāṁ viṣāsa̱him |

      ha̱ntāra̱ṁ śatrū̍ṇāṁ kṛdhi vi̱rāja̱ṁ gopa̍ti̱ṁ gavā̍m || 10.166.01

      a̱hama̍smi sapatna̱hendra̍ i̱vāri̍ṣṭo̱ akṣa̍taḥ |

      a̱dhaḥ sa̱patnā̍ me pa̱dori̱me sarve̍ a̱bhiṣṭhi̍tāḥ || 10.166.02

      atrai̱va vo'pi̍ nahyāmyu̱bhe ārtnī̍ iva̱ jyayā̍ |

      vāca̍spate̱ ni ṣe̍dhe̱mānyathā̱ madadha̍ra̱ṁ vadā̍n || 10.166.03

      a̱bhi̱bhūra̱hamāga̍maṁ vi̱śvaka̍rmeṇa̱ dhāmnā̍ |

      ā va̍ści̱ttamā vo̍ vra̱tamā vo̱'haṁ sami̍tiṁ dade || 10.166.04

      yo̱ga̱kṣe̱maṁ va̍ ā̱dāyā̱haṁ bhū̍yāsamutta̱ma ā vo̍ mū̱rdhāna̍makramīm |

      a̱dha̱spa̱dānma̱ udva̍data ma̱ṇḍūkā̍ ivoda̱kānma̱ṇḍūkā̍ uda̱kādi̍va || 10.166.05


      tubhye̱dami̍ndra̱ pari̍ ṣicyate̱ madhu̱ tvaṁ su̱tasya̍ ka̱laśa̍sya rājasi |

      tvaṁ ra̱yiṁ pu̍ru̱vīrā̍mu naskṛdhi̱ tvaṁ tapa̍ḥ pari̱tapyā̍jaya̱ḥ sva̍ḥ || 10.167.01

      sva̱rjita̱ṁ mahi̍ mandā̱namandha̍so̱ havā̍mahe̱ pari̍ śa̱kraṁ su̱tā upa̍ |

      i̱maṁ no̍ ya̱jñami̱ha bo̱dhyā ga̍hi̱ spṛdho̱ jaya̍ntaṁ ma̱ghavā̍namīmahe || 10.167.02

      soma̍sya̱ rājño̱ varu̍ṇasya̱ dharma̍ṇi̱ bṛha̱spate̱ranu̍matyā u̱ śarma̍ṇi |

      tavā̱hama̱dya ma̍ghava̱nnupa̍stutau̱ dhāta̱rvidhā̍taḥ ka̱laśā̍ abhakṣayam || 10.167.03

      prasū̍to bha̱kṣama̍karaṁ ca̱rāvapi̱ stoma̍ṁ ce̱maṁ pra̍tha̱maḥ sū̱rirunmṛ̍je |

      su̱te sā̱tena̱ yadyāga̍maṁ vā̱ṁ prati̍ viśvāmitrajamadagnī̱ dame̍ || 10.167.04


      vāta̍sya̱ nu ma̍hi̱māna̱ṁ ratha̍sya ru̱janne̍ti sta̱naya̍nnasya̱ ghoṣa̍ḥ |

      di̱vi̱spṛgyā̍tyaru̱ṇāni̍ kṛ̱ṇvannu̱to e̍ti pṛthi̱vyā re̱ṇumasya̍n || 10.168.01

      saṁ prera̍te̱ anu̱ vāta̍sya vi̱ṣṭhā aina̍ṁ gacchanti̱ sama̍na̱ṁ na yoṣā̍ḥ |

      tābhi̍ḥ sa̱yuksa̱ratha̍ṁ de̱va ī̍yate̱'sya viśva̍sya̱ bhuva̍nasya̱ rājā̍ || 10.168.02

      a̱ntari̍kṣe pa̱thibhi̱rīya̍māno̱ na ni vi̍śate kata̱macca̱nāha̍ḥ |

      a̱pāṁ sakhā̍ prathama̱jā ṛ̱tāvā̱ kva̍ svijjā̱taḥ kuta̱ ā ba̍bhūva || 10.168.03

      ā̱tmā de̱vānā̱ṁ bhuva̍nasya̱ garbho̍ yathāva̱śaṁ ca̍rati de̱va e̱ṣaḥ |

      ghoṣā̱ ida̍sya śṛṇvire̱ na rū̱paṁ tasmai̱ vātā̍ya ha̱viṣā̍ vidhema || 10.168.04


      ma̱yo̱bhūrvāto̍ a̱bhi vā̍tū̱srā ūrja̍svatī̱roṣa̍dhī̱rā ri̍śantām |

      pīva̍svatīrjī̱vadha̍nyāḥ pibantvava̱sāya̍ pa̱dvate̍ rudra mṛḻa || 10.169.01

      yāḥ sarū̍pā̱ virū̍pā̱ eka̍rūpā̱ yāsā̍ma̱gniriṣṭyā̱ nāmā̍ni̱ veda̍ |

      yā aṅgi̍rasa̱stapa̍se̱ha ca̱krustābhya̍ḥ parjanya̱ mahi̱ śarma̍ yaccha || 10.169.02

      yā de̱veṣu̍ ta̱nva1̱̍maira̍yanta̱ yāsā̱ṁ somo̱ viśvā̍ rū̱pāṇi̱ veda̍ |

      tā a̱smabhya̱ṁ paya̍sā̱ pinva̍mānāḥ pra̱jāva̍tīrindra go̱ṣṭhe ri̍rīhi || 10.169.03

      pra̱jāpa̍ti̱rmahya̍me̱tā rarā̍ṇo̱ viśvai̍rde̱vaiḥ pi̱tṛbhi̍ḥ saṁvidā̱naḥ |

      śi̱vāḥ sa̱tīrupa̍ no go̱ṣṭhamāka̱stāsā̍ṁ va̱yaṁ pra̱jayā̱ saṁ sa̍dema || 10.169.04


      vi̱bhrāḍbṛ̱hatpi̍batu so̱myaṁ madhvāyu̱rdadha̍dya̱jñapa̍tā̱vavi̍hrutam |

      vāta̍jūto̱ yo a̍bhi̱rakṣa̍ti̱ tmanā̍ pra̱jāḥ pu̍poṣa puru̱dhā vi rā̍jati || 10.170.01

      vi̱bhrāḍbṛ̱hatsubhṛ̍taṁ vāja̱sāta̍ma̱ṁ dharma̍ndi̱vo dha̱ruṇe̍ sa̱tyamarpi̍tam |

      a̱mi̱tra̱hā vṛ̍tra̱hā da̍syu̱hanta̍ma̱ṁ jyoti̍rjajñe asura̱hā sa̍patna̱hā || 10.170.02

      i̱daṁ śreṣṭha̱ṁ jyoti̍ṣā̱ṁ jyoti̍rutta̱maṁ vi̍śva̱jiddha̍na̱jidu̍cyate bṛ̱hat |

      vi̱śva̱bhrāḍbhrā̱jo mahi̱ sūryo̍ dṛ̱śa u̱ru pa̍prathe̱ saha̱ ojo̱ acyu̍tam || 10.170.03

      vi̱bhrāja̱ñjyoti̍ṣā̱ sva1̱̍raga̍ccho roca̱naṁ di̱vaḥ |

      yene̱mā viśvā̱ bhuva̍nā̱nyābhṛ̍tā vi̱śvaka̍rmaṇā vi̱śvade̍vyāvatā || 10.170.04


      tvaṁ tyami̱ṭato̱ ratha̱mindra̱ prāva̍ḥ su̱tāva̍taḥ |

      aśṛ̍ṇoḥ so̱mino̱ hava̍m || 10.171.01

      tvaṁ ma̱khasya̱ dodha̍ta̱ḥ śiro'va̍ tva̱co bha̍raḥ |

      aga̍cchaḥ so̱mino̍ gṛ̱ham || 10.171.02

      tvaṁ tyami̍ndra̱ martya̍māstrabu̱dhnāya̍ ve̱nyam |

      muhu̍ḥ śrathnā mana̱syave̍ || 10.171.03

      tvaṁ tyami̍ndra̱ sūrya̍ṁ pa̱ścā santa̍ṁ pu̱raskṛ̍dhi |

      de̱vānā̍ṁ citti̱ro vaśa̍m || 10.171.04


      ā yā̍hi̱ vana̍sā sa̱ha gāva̍ḥ sacanta varta̱niṁ yadūdha̍bhiḥ || 10.172.01

      ā yā̍hi̱ vasvyā̍ dhi̱yā maṁhi̍ṣṭho jāra̱yanma̍khaḥ su̱dānu̍bhiḥ || 10.172.02

      pi̱tu̱bhṛto̱ na tantu̱mitsu̱dāna̍va̱ḥ prati̍ dadhmo̱ yajā̍masi || 10.172.03

      u̱ṣā apa̱ svasu̱stama̱ḥ saṁ va̍rtayati varta̱niṁ su̍jā̱tatā̍ || 10.172.04


      ā tvā̍hārṣama̱ntare̍dhi dhru̱vasti̱ṣṭhāvi̍cācaliḥ |

      viśa̍stvā̱ sarvā̍ vāñchantu̱ mā tvadrā̱ṣṭramadhi̍ bhraśat || 10.173.01

      i̱haivaidhi̱ māpa̍ cyoṣṭhā̱ḥ parva̍ta i̱vāvi̍cācaliḥ |

      indra̍ ive̱ha dhru̱vasti̍ṣṭhe̱ha rā̱ṣṭramu̍ dhāraya || 10.173.02

      i̱mamindro̍ adīdharaddhru̱vaṁ dhru̱veṇa̍ ha̱viṣā̍ |

      tasmai̱ somo̱ adhi̍ brava̱ttasmā̍ u̱ brahma̍ṇa̱spati̍ḥ || 10.173.03

      dhru̱vā dyaurdhru̱vā pṛ̍thi̱vī dhru̱vāsa̱ḥ parva̍tā i̱me |

      dhru̱vaṁ viśva̍mi̱daṁ jaga̍ddhru̱vo rājā̍ vi̱śāma̱yam || 10.173.04

      dhru̱vaṁ te̱ rājā̱ varu̍ṇo dhru̱vaṁ de̱vo bṛha̱spati̍ḥ |

      dhru̱vaṁ ta̱ indra̍ścā̱gniśca̍ rā̱ṣṭraṁ dhā̍rayatāṁ dhru̱vam || 10.173.05

      dhru̱vaṁ dhru̱veṇa̍ ha̱viṣā̱bhi soma̍ṁ mṛśāmasi |

      atho̍ ta̱ indra̱ḥ keva̍lī̱rviśo̍ bali̱hṛta̍skarat || 10.173.06


      a̱bhī̱va̱rtena̍ ha̱viṣā̱ yenendro̍ abhivāvṛ̱te |

      tenā̱smānbra̍hmaṇaspate̱'bhi rā̱ṣṭrāya̍ vartaya || 10.174.01

      a̱bhi̱vṛtya̍ sa̱patnā̍na̱bhi yā no̱ arā̍tayaḥ |

      a̱bhi pṛ̍ta̱nyanta̍ṁ tiṣṭhā̱bhi yo na̍ ira̱syati̍ || 10.174.02

      a̱bhi tvā̍ de̱vaḥ sa̍vi̱tābhi somo̍ avīvṛtat |

      a̱bhi tvā̱ viśvā̍ bhū̱tānya̍bhīva̱rto yathāsa̍si || 10.174.03

      yenendro̍ ha̱viṣā̍ kṛ̱tvyabha̍vaddyu̱mnyu̍tta̱maḥ |

      i̱daṁ tada̍kri devā asapa̱tnaḥ kilā̍bhuvam || 10.174.04

      a̱sa̱pa̱tnaḥ sa̍patna̱hābhirā̍ṣṭro viṣāsa̱hiḥ |

      yathā̱hame̍ṣāṁ bhū̱tānā̍ṁ vi̱rājā̍ni̱ jana̍sya ca || 10.174.05


      pra vo̍ grāvāṇaḥ savi̱tā de̱vaḥ su̍vatu̱ dharma̍ṇā |

      dhū̱rṣu yu̍jyadhvaṁ sunu̱ta || 10.175.01

      grāvā̍ṇo̱ apa̍ du̱cchunā̱mapa̍ sedhata durma̱tim |

      u̱srāḥ ka̍rtana bheṣa̱jam || 10.175.02

      grāvā̍ṇa̱ upa̍re̱ṣvā ma̍hī̱yante̍ sa̱joṣa̍saḥ |

      vṛṣṇe̱ dadha̍to̱ vṛṣṇya̍m || 10.175.03

      grāvā̍ṇaḥ savi̱tā nu vo̍ de̱vaḥ su̍vatu̱ dharma̍ṇā |

      yaja̍mānāya sunva̱te || 10.175.04


      pra sū̱nava̍ ṛbhū̱ṇāṁ bṛ̱hanna̍vanta vṛ̱janā̍ |

      kṣāmā̱ ye vi̱śvadhā̍ya̱so'śna̍ndhe̱nuṁ na mā̱tara̍m || 10.176.01

      pra de̱vaṁ de̱vyā dhi̱yā bhara̍tā jā̱tave̍dasam |

      ha̱vyā no̍ vakṣadānu̱ṣak || 10.176.02

      a̱yamu̱ ṣya pra de̍va̱yurhotā̍ ya̱jñāya̍ nīyate |

      ratho̱ na yora̱bhīvṛ̍to̱ ghṛṇī̍vāñcetati̱ tmanā̍ || 10.176.03

      a̱yama̱gniru̍ruṣyatya̱mṛtā̍diva̱ janma̍naḥ |

      saha̍saści̱tsahī̍yānde̱vo jī̱vāta̍ve kṛ̱taḥ || 10.176.04


      pa̱ta̱ṁgama̱ktamasu̍rasya mā̱yayā̍ hṛ̱dā pa̍śyanti̱ mana̍sā vipa̱ścita̍ḥ |

      sa̱mu̱dre a̱ntaḥ ka̱vayo̱ vi ca̍kṣate̱ marī̍cīnāṁ pa̱dami̍cchanti ve̱dhasa̍ḥ || 10.177.01

      pa̱ta̱ṁgo vāca̱ṁ mana̍sā bibharti̱ tāṁ ga̍ndha̱rvo̍'vada̱dgarbhe̍ a̱ntaḥ |

      tāṁ dyota̍mānāṁ sva̱rya̍ṁ manī̱ṣāmṛ̱tasya̍ pa̱de ka̱vayo̱ ni pā̍nti || 10.177.02

      apa̍śyaṁ go̱pāmani̍padyamāna̱mā ca̱ parā̍ ca pa̱thibhi̱ścara̍ntam |

      sa sa̱dhrīcī̱ḥ sa viṣū̍cī̱rvasā̍na̱ ā va̍rīvarti̱ bhuva̍neṣva̱ntaḥ || 10.177.03


      tyamū̱ ṣu vā̱jina̍ṁ de̱vajū̍taṁ sa̱hāvā̍naṁ taru̱tāra̱ṁ rathā̍nām |

      ari̍ṣṭanemiṁ pṛta̱nāja̍mā̱śuṁ sva̱staye̱ tārkṣya̍mi̱hā hu̍vema || 10.178.01

      indra̍syeva rā̱timā̱johu̍vānāḥ sva̱staye̱ nāva̍mi̱vā ru̍hema |

      urvī̱ na pṛthvī̱ bahu̍le̱ gabhī̍re̱ mā vā̱metau̱ mā pare̍tau riṣāma || 10.178.02

      sa̱dyaści̱dyaḥ śava̍sā̱ pañca̍ kṛ̱ṣṭīḥ sūrya̍ iva̱ jyoti̍ṣā̱pasta̱tāna̍ |

      sa̱ha̱sra̱sāḥ śa̍ta̱sā a̍sya̱ raṁhi̱rna smā̍ varante yuva̱tiṁ na śaryā̍m || 10.178.03


      utti̍ṣṭha̱tāva̍ paśya̱tendra̍sya bhā̱gamṛ̱tviya̍m |

      yadi̍ śrā̱to ju̱hota̍na̱ yadyaśrā̍to mama̱ttana̍ || 10.179.01

      śrā̱taṁ ha̱viro ṣvi̍ndra̱ pra yā̍hi ja̱gāma̱ sūro̱ adhva̍no̱ vima̍dhyam |

      pari̍ tvāsate ni̱dhibhi̱ḥ sakhā̍yaḥ kula̱pā na vrā̱japa̍ti̱ṁ cara̍ntam || 10.179.02

      śrā̱taṁ ma̍nya̱ ūdha̍ni śrā̱tama̱gnau suśrā̍taṁ manye̱ tadṛ̱taṁ navī̍yaḥ |

      mādhya̍ṁdinasya̱ sava̍nasya da̱dhnaḥ pibe̍ndra vajrinpurukṛjjuṣā̱ṇaḥ || 10.179.03


      pra sa̍sāhiṣe puruhūta̱ śatrū̱ñjyeṣṭha̍ste̱ śuṣma̍ i̱ha rā̱tira̍stu |

      indrā bha̍ra̱ dakṣi̍ṇenā̱ vasū̍ni̱ pati̱ḥ sindhū̍nāmasi re̱vatī̍nām || 10.180.01

      mṛ̱go na bhī̱maḥ ku̍ca̱ro gi̍ri̱ṣṭhāḥ pa̍rā̱vata̱ ā ja̍ganthā̱ para̍syāḥ |

      sṛ̱kaṁ sa̱ṁśāya̍ pa̱vimi̍ndra ti̱gmaṁ vi śatrū̍ntāḻhi̱ vi mṛdho̍ nudasva || 10.180.02

      indra̍ kṣa̱trama̱bhi vā̱mamojo'jā̍yathā vṛṣabha carṣaṇī̱nām |

      apā̍nudo̱ jana̍mamitra̱yanta̍mu̱ruṁ de̱vebhyo̍ akṛṇoru lo̱kam || 10.180.03


      pratha̍śca̱ yasya̍ sa̱pratha̍śca̱ nāmānu̍ṣṭubhasya ha̱viṣo̍ ha̱viryat |

      dhā̱turdyutā̍nātsavi̱tuśca̱ viṣṇo̍ rathaṁta̱ramā ja̍bhārā̱ vasi̍ṣṭhaḥ || 10.181.01

      avi̍nda̱nte ati̍hita̱ṁ yadāsī̍dya̱jñasya̱ dhāma̍ para̱maṁ guhā̱ yat |

      dhā̱turdyutā̍nātsavi̱tuśca̱ viṣṇo̍rbha̱radvā̍jo bṛ̱hadā ca̍kre a̱gneḥ || 10.181.02

      te̍'vinda̱nmana̍sā̱ dīdhyā̍nā̱ yaju̍ḥ ṣka̱nnaṁ pra̍tha̱maṁ de̍va̱yāna̍m |

      dhā̱turdyutā̍nātsavi̱tuśca̱ viṣṇo̱rā sūryā̍dabharangha̱rmame̱te || 10.181.03


      bṛha̱spati̍rnayatu du̱rgahā̍ ti̱raḥ puna̍rneṣada̱ghaśa̍ṁsāya̱ manma̍ |

      kṣi̱padaśa̍sti̱mapa̍ durma̱tiṁ ha̱nnathā̍ kara̱dyaja̍mānāya̱ śaṁ yoḥ || 10.182.01

      narā̱śaṁso̍ no'vatu prayā̱je śaṁ no̍ astvanuyā̱jo have̍ṣu |

      kṣi̱padaśa̍sti̱mapa̍ durma̱tiṁ ha̱nnathā̍ kara̱dyaja̍mānāya̱ śaṁ yoḥ || 10.182.02

      tapu̍rmūrdhā tapatu ra̱kṣaso̱ ye bra̍hma̱dviṣa̱ḥ śara̍ve̱ hanta̱vā u̍ |

      kṣi̱padaśa̍sti̱mapa̍ durma̱tiṁ ha̱nnathā̍ kara̱dyaja̍mānāya̱ śaṁ yoḥ || 10.182.03


      apa̍śyaṁ tvā̱ mana̍sā̱ ceki̍tāna̱ṁ tapa̍so jā̱taṁ tapa̍so̱ vibhū̍tam |

      i̱ha pra̱jāmi̱ha ra̱yiṁ rarā̍ṇa̱ḥ pra jā̍yasva pra̱jayā̍ putrakāma || 10.183.01

      apa̍śyaṁ tvā̱ mana̍sā̱ dīdhyā̍nā̱ṁ svāyā̍ṁ ta̱nū ṛtvye̱ nādha̍mānām |

      upa̱ māmu̱ccā yu̍va̱tirba̍bhūyā̱ḥ pra jā̍yasva pra̱jayā̍ putrakāme || 10.183.02

      a̱haṁ garbha̍madadhā̱moṣa̍dhīṣva̱haṁ viśve̍ṣu̱ bhuva̍neṣva̱ntaḥ |

      a̱haṁ pra̱jā a̍janayaṁ pṛthi̱vyāma̱haṁ jani̍bhyo apa̱rīṣu̍ pu̱trān || 10.183.03


      viṣṇu̱ryoni̍ṁ kalpayatu̱ tvaṣṭā̍ rū̱pāṇi̍ piṁśatu |

      ā si̍ñcatu pra̱jāpa̍tirdhā̱tā garbha̍ṁ dadhātu te || 10.184.01

      garbha̍ṁ dhehi sinīvāli̱ garbha̍ṁ dhehi sarasvati |

      garbha̍ṁ te a̱śvinau̍ de̱vāvā dha̍ttā̱ṁ puṣka̍rasrajā || 10.184.02

      hi̱ra̱ṇyayī̍ a̱raṇī̱ yaṁ ni̱rmantha̍to a̱śvinā̍ |

      taṁ te̱ garbha̍ṁ havāmahe daśa̱me mā̱si sūta̍ve || 10.184.03


      mahi̍ trī̱ṇāmavo̍'stu dyu̱kṣaṁ mi̱trasyā̍rya̱mṇaḥ |

      du̱rā̱dharṣa̱ṁ varu̍ṇasya || 10.185.01

      na̱hi teṣā̍ma̱mā ca̱na nādhva̍su vāra̱ṇeṣu̍ |

      īśe̍ ri̱pura̱ghaśa̍ṁsaḥ || 10.185.02

      yasmai̍ pu̱trāso̱ adi̍te̱ḥ pra jī̱vase̱ martyā̍ya |

      jyoti̱ryaccha̱ntyaja̍sram || 10.185.03


      vāta̱ ā vā̍tu bheṣa̱jaṁ śa̱mbhu ma̍yo̱bhu no̍ hṛ̱de |

      pra ṇa̱ āyū̍ṁṣi tāriṣat || 10.186.01

      u̱ta vā̍ta pi̱tāsi̍ na u̱ta bhrāto̱ta na̱ḥ sakhā̍ |

      sa no̍ jī̱vāta̍ve kṛdhi || 10.186.02

      yada̱do vā̍ta te gṛ̱he̱3̱̍'mṛta̍sya ni̱dhirhi̱taḥ |

      tato̍ no dehi jī̱vase̍ || 10.186.03


      prāgnaye̱ vāca̍mīraya vṛṣa̱bhāya̍ kṣitī̱nām |

      sa na̍ḥ parṣa̱dati̱ dviṣa̍ḥ || 10.187.01

      yaḥ para̍syāḥ parā̱vata̍sti̱ro dhanvā̍ti̱roca̍te |

      sa na̍ḥ parṣa̱dati̱ dviṣa̍ḥ || 10.187.02

      yo rakṣā̍ṁsi ni̱jūrva̍ti̱ vṛṣā̍ śu̱kreṇa̍ śo̱ciṣā̍ |

      sa na̍ḥ parṣa̱dati̱ dviṣa̍ḥ || 10.187.03

      yo viśvā̱bhi vi̱paśya̍ti̱ bhuva̍nā̱ saṁ ca̱ paśya̍ti |

      sa na̍ḥ parṣa̱dati̱ dviṣa̍ḥ || 10.187.04

      yo a̱sya pā̱re raja̍saḥ śu̱kro a̱gnirajā̍yata |

      sa na̍ḥ parṣa̱dati̱ dviṣa̍ḥ || 10.187.05


      pra nū̱naṁ jā̱tave̍dasa̱maśva̍ṁ hinota vā̱jina̍m |

      i̱daṁ no̍ ba̱rhirā̱sade̍ || 10.188.01

      a̱sya pra jā̱tave̍daso̱ vipra̍vīrasya mī̱ḻhuṣa̍ḥ |

      ma̱hīmi̍yarmi suṣṭu̱tim || 10.188.02

      yā ruco̍ jā̱tave̍daso deva̱trā ha̍vya̱vāha̍nīḥ |

      tābhi̍rno ya̱jñami̍nvatu || 10.188.03


      āyaṁ gauḥ pṛśni̍rakramī̱dasa̍danmā̱tara̍ṁ pu̱raḥ |

      pi̱tara̍ṁ ca pra̱yansva̍ḥ || 10.189.01

      a̱ntaśca̍rati roca̱nāsya prā̱ṇāda̍pāna̱tī |

      vya̍khyanmahi̱ṣo diva̍m || 10.189.02

      tri̱ṁśaddhāma̱ vi rā̍jati̱ vākpa̍ta̱ṁgāya̍ dhīyate |

      prati̱ vasto̱raha̱ dyubhi̍ḥ || 10.189.03


      ṛ̱taṁ ca̍ sa̱tyaṁ cā̱bhī̍ddhā̱ttapa̱so'dhya̍jāyata |

      tato̱ rātrya̍jāyata̱ tata̍ḥ samu̱dro a̍rṇa̱vaḥ || 10.190.01

      sa̱mu̱drāda̍rṇa̱vādadhi̍ saṁvatsa̱ro a̍jāyata |

      a̱ho̱rā̱trāṇi̍ vi̱dadha̱dviśva̍sya miṣa̱to va̱śī || 10.190.02

      sū̱ryā̱ca̱ndra̱masau̍ dhā̱tā ya̍thāpū̱rvama̍kalpayat |

      diva̍ṁ ca pṛthi̱vīṁ cā̱ntari̍kṣa̱matho̱ sva̍ḥ || 10.190.03


      saṁsa̱midyu̍vase vṛṣa̱nnagne̱ viśvā̍nya̱rya ā |

      i̱ḻaspa̱de sami̍dhyase̱ sa no̱ vasū̱nyā bha̍ra || 10.191.01

      saṁ ga̍cchadhva̱ṁ saṁ va̍dadhva̱ṁ saṁ vo̱ manā̍ṁsi jānatām |

      de̱vā bhā̱gaṁ yathā̱ pūrve̍ saṁjānā̱nā u̱pāsa̍te || 10.191.02

      sa̱mā̱no mantra̱ḥ sami̍tiḥ samā̱nī sa̍mā̱naṁ mana̍ḥ sa̱ha ci̱ttame̍ṣām |

      sa̱mā̱naṁ mantra̍ma̱bhi ma̍ntraye vaḥ samā̱nena̍ vo ha̱viṣā̍ juhomi || 10.191.03

      sa̱mā̱nī va̱ ākū̍tiḥ samā̱nā hṛda̍yāni vaḥ |

      sa̱mā̱nama̍stu vo̱ mano̱ yathā̍ va̱ḥ susa̱hāsa̍ti || 10.191.04


      Last udpated July 2, 2013


      Special mention : Initial processing and help by Avinash and Shashi Sathaye,

      Avinash Chopde, Shree Devi Kumar, Sunder Hattangadi, John Gardner.

      Reprocessed from Original in final form by Detlef Eichler with additional corrections.

      See Detlef's site http://www.detlef108.de/Rigveda.htm

      for other details and formats.


      The text is shown with accents (Anudattas, dependent Svaritas,

      and independent Svaritas including Kampas). Words are connected (agnimILe).

      Ch is doubled as in gachChati according to the rules of Rigveda-Pratishakhya.

      At the end of a word m is replaced by Anusvara M if the initial letter of the

      following word is a labial stop consonant (p, ph, b, bh, m).

      Visarga H before sh, Sh or s followed by a voiceless consonant has been restored.


      Source : The Aufrecht/van Nooten/Holland (Samhita) version

      of the Rigveda (http://www.people.fas.harvard.edu/~witzel/onlineRV.htm).

      In this text accented vowels have Udatta or 'independent Svarita' markers.

      Kampas are not shown. Words are separated (agnim ILe).

      Ch is not doubled as in gaChati. At the end of a word we find m before

      a following labial stop consonant (p, ph, b, bh, m).

      Visarga H before sh, Sh or s followed by a voiceless consonant has

      been dropped according to a rule of Rigveda-Pratishakhya.
